emails.title: Improve your coding skills with 30 Days of Code
emails.Text: Ready to become a better coder? Practicing for a programming job interview? Join thousands of other HackerRank members who are learning to code or brushing up on fundamentals. Each day, you’ll get a new code challenge and a corresponding video tutorial to help you learn.
